    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;}\n.html-preview .Text {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview .a4 {className: a4; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 8pt; text-indent: 48px;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-weight: bold;\">Пропискага қўйишга розилик тўғрисида ариза</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#2}Ариза берилаётган ташкилот номи </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">га</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}Аризачининг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">,</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#8}Аризачининг яшаётган уйи рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">-уйда яшовчи</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#9}Аризачининг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> дан</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">(паспорт </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">{#10}Аризачининг паспорт серия рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">{#11}Аризачига паспорт берилган худуд</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\"> томонидан</span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">{#12}Аризачига паспорт берилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-style: italic;\"> йилда берилган)</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: right;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: right;\"></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 5.65pt; margin-bottom: 5.65pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #auto;\">А<span class=\"leading\"></span>Р И З А</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси, </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#5}Аризачининг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> ,</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#14}Ариза берилган сана</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 26.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Мен – </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#9}Аризачининг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> ўзимга тегишли бўлган </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#5}Аризачининг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#8}Аризачининг яшаётган уйи рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">-сонли уй-жойимга – </span><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#15}Пропискага қўйилаётган шахс фарзандининг туғилган санаси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> йилда туғилган фарзандим </span><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#16}Пропискага қўйилаётган шахснинг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">ни (паспорт </span><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#17}Пропискага қўйилаётган шахснинг паспорт серияси рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#18}Паспорт берган ИИБ номи </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#19}Паспорт берилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> йилда берилган) доимий яшаш учун пропискага қўйишга розилик бераман.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 26.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Кейинчалик ҳеч қандай моддий ва мулкий даъво қилмайман.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 26.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Аризанинг матнини тўлиқ ўқиб чиқдик, унинг мазмуни ва моҳияти, ҳуқуқий оқибатлари менга нотариус томонидан тушунтирилди ва тушунарли, аризанинг мазмуни менинг асл хоҳиш-истакларимга мос келади.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Ариза берувчи: ___________________________________________________</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Нотариуснинг тасдиқлов ёзуви</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n</div></div>",
